user_description: Together with our GP members we deliver improved healthcare, closer to home for the North Tyneside community. Tweets by Dr Eleanor Holmes & Ethan @intoitmediauk
text:
A reminder that booster doses of the #CovidVaccine can now be booked a month in advance. The NHS online booking system will allow people to book their booster from 5 months after their 2nd dose. So far more than a million bookings have already been made. 

https://t.co/1FtjCh5Lmq

So, I'm sat waiting my 15 mins after my Covid19 booster vaccine but my mind is drifting - booster, booster button, turbo booster, jet pack booster, rocket booster - wait a minute, there's a story here!

#WritingCommunity #scifi #scifibooks #CovidVaccine
